	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65437497">It is worth noting even the easiest puzzles here are puzzles which many, if not most humans, cannot solve. The fact that we're now evaluating AI reasoning based on puzzles above human baseline should itself be pretty alarming. But instead we've moved the goalposts and so are reassuring ourselves that the AIs cannot easily solve genuinely tricky puzzles.</div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_65437497">
<span class="ind"></span><a id="reply_link_65437497" class="btn link" href="//apple.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23713767&amp;op=Reply&amp;threshold=1&amp;commentsort=0&amp;mode=thread&amp;pid=65437497" onclick="D2.replyTo(65437497); return false;">Reply to This</a> 	<a rel="nofollow" href="#" class="comment_share_toggle btn link">Share</a>
	<div class="comment_share sharethis-0 hide"><span class="au"></span>
